OL,3,CResident doctors in England to strike
OL,4,Cfor six days
OL,6,FResident doctors in England are to
OL,7,Fbegin a six-day walkout as the row
OL,8,Fwith the Government over jobs and pay
OL,9,Fintensifies.
OL,11,FTens of thousands of resident doctors,
OL,12,Fformerly known as junior doctors, will
OL,13,Fdown their stethoscopes from 7am on
OL,14,FApril 7.
OL,16,FNHS officials have said the strike
OL,17,Fwill be "difficult" but urged patients
OL,18,Fto come forward as normal.
OL,26,@yD@IOUyD@SO]
