OL,3,CResident doctors in England to strike
OL,4,Cfor six days
OL,6,FHealth leaders said the walkout will
OL,7,Fbe "challenging due to the shorter
OL,8,Fnotice period" and because of the
OL,9,Faction taking place during the Easter
OL,10,Fholiday, when many NHS staff will have
OL,11,Fbooked time off with their families.
OL,13,FNHS England said that it will keep as
OL,14,Fmuch pre-planned care running as
OL,15,Fpossible, and patients are urged to
OL,16,Fattend appointments unless they have
OL,17,Fbeen contacted.
OL,19,FUrgent and emergency care will run as
OL,20,Fusual.
OL,26,@oD@DOUpD@NO]
