CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775653863
OL,3,CResident doctors in England to strike
OL,4,Cfor six days
OL,6,F"We know this round of industrial
OL,7,Faction will be difficult, coming
OL,8,Fstraight after the Easter weekend, but
OL,9,Fpatients should come forward as normal
OL,10,Fand attend any appointments unless
OL,11,Fthey are contacted otherwise," NHS
OL,12,FEngland's Professor Ramani Moonesinghe
OL,13,Fsaid on Monday.
OL,15,FMr Streeting said that the strike was
OL,16,F"disappointing", adding: "My attention
OL,17,Fand that of leaders across the NHS is
OL,18,Fnow on protecting patients and staff
OL,19,Fby minimising disruption to the health
OL,20,Fservice."
