PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775653863
OL,3,CResident doctors in England to strike
OL,4,Cfor six days
OL,6,FDr Jack Fletcher, chairman of the
OL,7,FBMA's resident doctors committee, said
OL,8,Fthe Government "quietly watered down"
OL,9,Fthe deal on offer to resident doctors.
OL,11,FHe added: "Resident doctors are as
OL,12,Fkeen as he is to bring an end to the
OL,13,Fstrikes, but his Government needs to
OL,14,Fput an offer on the table that we can
OL,15,Faccept and which doesn't change at the
OL,16,Flast minute."
OL,18,FThe latest strike is the 15th walkout
OL,19,Fby resident doctors in England since
OL,20,F2023.
OL,26,@pD@POUpD@eO]sD@KOUxD@MO]
