CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1775653863
OL,3,CResident doctors in England to strike
OL,4,Cfor six days
OL,6,FElsewhere, hundreds of BMA staff are
OL,7,Falso on strike in an ongoing row over
OL,8,Fpay.
OL,10,FThe 48-hour walkout started on Monday.
OL,12,FAnd last week it emerged that senior
OL,13,Fmedics will also be balloted on
OL,14,Findustrial action after ministers
OL,15,Fannounced a 3.5% pay award.
OL,17,FSimultaneous ballots of consultants
OL,18,Fand specialist, associate specialist
OL,19,Fand specialty (SAS) doctors will run
OL,20,Ffrom May 11 until July 6.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
